---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Commercial & Storefront Cleaning | Felt Pressure Washing" description="Professional commercial exterior cleaning in Eugene, Springfield and surrounding areas. Keep your business looking its best.">
  <section class="service-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-icon-lg">üè¢</div>
      <h1 class="section-title">Commercial & Storefront Cleaning</h1>
      <p class="section-subtitle">Keep your business looking professional and welcoming</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-details">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="service-content">
        <h2>First Impressions Matter</h2>
        <p>
          Your building's exterior is the first thing customers see. Dirty walls, stained sidewalks, and
          grimy storefronts can turn people away before they even walk through the door. Regular exterior
          cleaning keeps your property looking professional and inviting.
        </p>
        <p>
          We work with businesses of all sizes ‚Äî from small storefronts to larger commercial buildings.
          We can schedule cleanings around your business hours to minimize disruption, and we offer
          recurring maintenance plans to keep your property looking great year-round.
        </p>

        <h3>Commercial Services</h3>
        <ul class="service-list">
          <li>Building exterior and facades</li>
          <li>Storefronts and entryways</li>
          <li>Sidewalks and parking areas</li>
          <li>Dumpster pads and loading areas</li>
          <li>Drive-throughs and service areas</li>
          <li>Recurring maintenance programs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="faq-section">
    <div class="container">
      <h2 class="section-title">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="faq-list">
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can you work around our business hours?</summary>
          <p>Absolutely. We regularly schedule cleanings during early mornings, evenings, or weekends to avoid disrupting your customers and employees. We'll find a time that works for your business.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you offer recurring commercial cleaning?</summary>
          <p>Yes! We offer monthly, quarterly, and annual maintenance plans. Regular cleaning keeps your property consistently clean and can be more cost-effective than one-off deep cleans.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Can you clean multi-story buildings?</summary>
          <p>We can clean buildings up to 3 stories using our professional equipment. For taller buildings, we can discuss options and may be able to accommodate your needs.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Will pressure washing remove graffiti?</summary>
          <p>In many cases, yes. Depending on the paint type and surface material, pressure washing combined with appropriate solvents can remove most graffiti. We'll assess the situation and let you know what to expect.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="faq-item">
          <summary>Do you carry insurance for commercial jobs?</summary>
          <p>Yes, we are fully insured. We carry liability insurance that covers both residential and commercial work, so you can have peace of mind during the cleaning process.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="service-cta">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Keep Your Business Looking Sharp</h2>
        <p>Get a free estimate today ‚Äî no obligation, no pressure.</p>
        <a href="/#estimate" class="btn btn-primary">Get Free Estimate</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<style>
  .service-hero {
    padding: 60px 0 30px;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #F0F9FF 0%, #E0F2FE 100%);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .service-icon-lg {
    font-size: 48px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .service-details {
    padding: 50px 0;
  }

  .service-content h2 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 28px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
  }

  .service-content h3 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 700;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    margin-top: 32px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .service-content p {
    color: var(--light-gray);
    line-height: 1.8;
    font-size: 16px;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    max-width: 800px;
  }

  .service-list {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
  }

  .service-list li {
    padding: 10px 0;
    padding-left: 28px;
    position: relative;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    font-weight: 500;
    border-bottom: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
  }

  .service-list li::before {
    content: '‚úì';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--success);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  .faq-section {
    padding: 50px 0;
    background: var(--bg-light);
  }

  .faq-list {
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .faq-item {
    background: white;
    border-radius: 10px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    border: 1px solid #E5E7EB;
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: box-shadow 0.3s ease;
  }

  .faq-item:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }

  .faq-item[open] {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--light-blue);
  }

  .faq-item summary {
    padding: 18px 24px;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--dark-gray);
    cursor: pointer;
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: space-between;
    align-items: center;
    font-size: 16px;
  }

  .faq-item summary::-webkit-details-marker {
    display: none;
  }

  .faq-item summary::after {
    content: '+';
    font-size: 22px;
    font-weight: 300;
    color: var(--primary-blue);
    transition: transform 0.3s ease;
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-left: 16px;
  }

  .faq-item[open] summary::after {
    content: '‚àí';
  }

  .faq-item p {
    padding: 0 24px 18px;
    color: var(--light-gray);
    line-height: 1.7;
    font-size: 15px;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .service-cta {
    padding: 50px 0;
  }

  .cta-block {
    text-align: center;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), var(--accent-blue));
    color: var(--white);
    padding: 48px 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
  }

  .cta-block h2 {
    font-family: 'Montserrat', sans-serif;
    font-size: 32px;
    font-weight: 700;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .cta-block p {
    font-size: 18px;
    opacity: 0.9;
    margin-bottom: 32px;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .service-hero {
      padding: 60px 0 30px;
    }

    .service-content h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .cta-block {
      padding: 40px 24px;
    }

    .cta-block h2 {
      font-size: 24px;
    }

    .faq-item summary {
      font-size: 15px;
      padding: 16px 20px;
    }

    .faq-item p {
      padding: 0 20px 16px;
      font-size: 14px;
    }
  }
</style>
